{"lemma":"مُحَمَّرُو","slug":"مُحَمَّرُو","root":"ح.م.ر","root_slug":"ح-م-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-م-ر","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n9088"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D8%AD%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%B1%D9%8F%D9%88"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"roasted; fried"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the passive participle of the verb حَمَّرَ (ḥammara)."},"ipa":["/mu.ħam.mar/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n9088","headword_ar":"مِحْمَرٌ","root":"Hmr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miHolaA^N","text_ar":"مِحْلَاٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K; in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miHolA'","text_ar":"مِحْلاء"},{"kind":"text","text":";) i. e. The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"iron instrument,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stone, with which one shaves off the hair and dirt on the surface of a hide, and with which one skins."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, TA. [But for the last words of the explanation in those two lexicons,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yn$f bh","text_ar":"ينشف به"},{"kind":"text","text":", I read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yunotaqu bihi","text_ar":"يُنْتَقُ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":".])       -A2-  Also, (S, TA,) in the K, [and in a copy of the A,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHam~arN","text_ar":"مَحَمَّرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is a mistake, (TA,) A horse"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"got by a stallion of generous,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Arabian, race, out of a mare not of such a race;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not of generous birth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a jade;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hajiynN","text_ar":"هَجِينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, A, K;) in Persian,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"PaAlaAniYo","text_ar":"پَالَانِىْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ham~aArapN","text_ar":"حَمَّارَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or a horse"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of mean race, that resembles the ass in his slowness of running:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bad"},{"kind":"text","text":"beast: (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHaAmiru","text_ar":"مَحَامِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHaAmiyru","text_ar":"مَحَامِيرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and accord. to the T, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ham~aArapN","text_ar":"حَمَّارَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies [not as it is explained above, as a sing., but]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHaAmiru","text_ar":"مَحَامِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and Z explains it as an epithet applied to horses, signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that run like asses."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  Also An"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ignoble,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"man: (K, * TA:) and a man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who will not give unless pressed and importuned."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","TA","K","A"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}